sources.description:
MARSHAL of LAW...MASTER of MEN...he fights for right and the girl he loves!
Rogers plays a look-alike to the dead Billy The Kid and restores the tranquility of Lincoln County after subduing the criminal element.

Director: Joseph Kane (as Joe Kane)
Writer: Jack Natteford
Stars: Roy Rogers, Smiley Burnette, Lynne Roberts 
Genres: Action, Musical, Romance, Western
